Output output/move_bookmark.gif
Output output/move_bookmark.webm

Require jjui
Require jj

Set Theme Dracula
Set Padding 0
Set FontSize 20
Set Width 1000
Set Height 600
Set Framerate 24
Set WindowBarSize 0

Hide
Type "jjui repo/" Enter
Wait /normal/
Show
Sleep 0.5s

Type@1.5s "bm"
Sleep 1s
Enter
Sleep 1s
Hide
Type "q"
